      <p>At BenixSpace, accessible from https://benix.space, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors and users. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by BenixSpace and how we use it.</p>
      
      <p>If you have additional questions or require more information about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us through email at benirabok@gmail.com</p>
      
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      
      <p>When you register for a BenixSpace account or use our services, we may collect several different types of information for various purposes to provide and improve our Service to you:</p>
      
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone numbers, physical address, payment information, etc.</li>
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username, password, account preferences, and profile settings.</li>
        <li><strong>Transaction Information:</strong> Details about purchases, clicks, shares, commissions earned, and other transaction details when you use our Services.</li>
        <li><strong>Log Data:</strong> Information that your browser sends whenever you visit our website, including your computer's IP address, browser type and version, pages you visit, time and date of your visit, time spent on those pages, and other statistics.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies and Usage Data:</strong> We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to track activity on our Service and hold certain information. Cookies are files with small amount of data which may include an anonymous unique identifier.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      
      <p>We use the collected information for various purposes:</p>
      
      <ul>
        <li>To provide and maintain our Service</li>
        <li>To notify you about changes to our Service</li>
        <li>To allow you to participate in interactive features of our Service when you choose to do so</li>
        <li>To provide customer support</li>
        <li>To gather analysis or valuable information so that we can improve our Service</li>
        <li>To monitor the usage of our Service</li>
        <li>To detect, prevent and address technical issues</li>
        <li>To process payments and track commission earnings</li>
        <li>To deliver targeted advertisements</li>
        <li>To communicate with you about your account, services, promotions, and events</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Google AdSense</h2>
      
      <p>We use Google AdSense to serve advertisements on our website. Google AdSense may use cookies and web beacons to collect information about your visits to this and other websites to provide relevant advertisements about goods and services that may interest you.</p>
      
      <p>Google AdSense also uses DART cookies which enables it to serve ads to users based on their visit to our site and other sites on the Internet. You may opt out of the use of the DART cookie by visiting the Google ad and content network privacy policy at: https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads</p>
      
      <p>Our advertising partners, including Google, may use cookies and web beacons to collect information about your activities on this and other websites to provide you with targeted advertising based on your browsing activities and interests.</p>
      
      <h2>4. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
      
      <p>We may disclose your Personal Information in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to:</p>
      
      <ul>
        <li>Comply with a legal obligation</li>
        <li>Protect and defend the rights or property of BenixSpace and NebeluRw</li>
        <li>Prevent or investigate possible wrongdoing in connection with the Service</li>
        <li>Protect the personal safety of users of the Service or the public</li>
        <li>Protect against legal liability</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>We may share your information with:</p>
      
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We may employ third-party companies and individuals to facilitate our Service, provide the Service on our behalf, perform Service-related services, or assist us in analyzing how our Service is used. These third parties have access to your Personal Information only to perform these tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.</li>
        <li><strong>Merchants and Affiliate Partners:</strong> We share necessary information with merchants and affiliate partners to facilitate transactions, track conversions, and process commissions.</li>
        <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> If BenixSpace is involved in a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, your Personal Information may be transferred.</li>
